name: CATCOIN NFT - 1'000'000 CAT Coins
description:
CATCOIN.ch is a meme-coin-project with the goal to create a CAT-coin and many other things related to this coin. 

We can't promise you anything and in the worst case you have to expect a total loss, but if we are successful, the plan is that we will take back the NFT's and exchange them for a corresponding number of CAT Coins.

-------------------------

A total of 15 of this NFT will be issued. We would like to point out once again that this is not a serious project and that a total loss must be expected.
